subject: Basketball (College)
College Athletics
Antitrust Laws and Competition Issues
lead_paragraph: The N.C.A.A. notified the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit that it intended to appeal a judge’s ruling in the Ed O’Bannon case that it had violated antitrust laws.
